        <mxCell id="aYawBRkTkJilWXz14I1b-15" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="- Choose langusge(Dutch, English)&lt;div&gt;- Max 1 A4 Paper&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Sound Human&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Option to add some detailes:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Graduate student&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Minor in .....&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- A reference&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Save ML as [Name]space[companyname]space[Motivational letter]&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
